      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in showroom-original condition. This vehicle represents the zenith of automotive preservation, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains entirely unblemished. Meticulously curated and mechanically peerless, this unit offers a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to secure an investment-grade asset that transcends standard market offerings.",
