    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true time-capsule specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless factory finish with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. The interior remains in showroom state, featuring supple, uncreased leather and the distinct aroma of a new car. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete binder of documentation included. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched alloy wheels wrapped in premium rubber, this car is mechanically and aesthetically indistinguishable from the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
