      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total beauty. This car is in showroom condition\u2014seriously, not a single scratch or dent anywhere! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and still feels brand new. If you're looking for perfection, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
